			<attribute id="synopsis" type="LSString" value="2 Fists got an extreme training as a form of punisment. A commander is observing them. This is the equivalent of &quot;drop and give me twenty&quot; except she wants like twenty thousand. From time to time the 2 Fists get weakened, as they are on the brink of exhaustion, and say a random line from this pool. Alll lines involve heavy panting. " />
